# Create Your Own Fabric App: End-to-End Tutorial

This tutorial teaches you how to build a production-ready Microsoft Fabric Analytics web app from scratch using GitHub Copilot, Rayfin, and Fabric App Data packages. You'll learn the pattern by building a complete example, then customize it for your own data and use case.

**What You'll Learn:**
- How to scaffold a Rayfin + Fabric app using Copilot
- How to connect to your own Fabric semantic model
- How to design and query your semantic model tables
- How to build custom dashboards and KPIs
- How to deploy to Fabric

